stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> inactive: Slot 创建
    inactive --> active: 消费者连接
    active --> active: 解码 + ACK
    active --> inactive: 正常断开
    inactive --> extended: WAL 超过普通保留但仍被 Slot 保留
    inactive --> lost: 所需 WAL 被移除/Slot 失效
    active --> invalid: Catalog Xmin/WAL/参数等导致失效
    lost --> [*]: Drop + Resnapshot
    invalid --> [*]: Drop + Resnapshot
